><br />\n<br />\n無主見指大事定小事先？<br />\n小事嘅話，我都好無主見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n大小事都要有 要比到人一種好firm嘅感覺 可靠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔會畀人話獨裁？"},{"pid":"96e7ad9e6b8778fef0d8be824ae2381ccede5aeb","tid":368051,"uid":118218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T05:53:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>食軟飯 呃女錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc14a9bc0341cbab1cd15cf4b998803f9fdbc263","tid":368051,"uid":118218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T05:55:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>八婆格 玩office politics 搵唔到錢 老婆奴 溝唔到女 見識少</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n啲臭雞格嘅女真係想大巴大巴煎死佢地<br />\n<br />\n搵唔到錢呢個有待商榷<br />\n<br />\n呀媽話怕老婆會發達<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  我想發達<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n溝唔到女，唉這些機會<br />\n<br />\n見識少呢樣真，明明世界咁大，都唔識去睇多啲唔同嘅野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f54e11cb0bf19a75981e6996087fe7717ca3509b","tid":368051,"uid":116422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T06:05:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點嘅人生先可以畀人稱為垃圾？<br />\n點嘅男人先會畀人話係廢柴？<br />\n<br />\n真係學啲港女話嘅無上進心無錢無樓咁表面？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n1。無盡力做過事，做事怕辛苦。失業？？咁有無搵過工，餐廳辛苦唔做，做地盤日曬雨淋又唔做，文職又話悶唔做，創業又話無錢，又唔諗點去做。<br />\n2。三分鐘熱度。 無恒心，唔想去等待享受辛苦過後嘅成果。<br />\n3。冇責任心， 日日諗住點樣將啲責任逃避，唔去主動承擔責任。<br />\n4。 怕俾人拒絕而唔去主動，不過只要放下唔值錢嘅自尊心。其實識朋友，結交知已一啲都唔難。<br />\n5。做事無決斷力， 優柔寡斷，決而不行&hellip;唔洗講咁多啦<br />\n6。 短視 做咩都要求即刻有回報， 唔去諗將來嘅成果。<br />\n7。 對朋友對工作對人無一份忠誠， 成日諗住點樣佔人便宜<br />\n8。自視過高， 成日覺得自己懷才不遇，孤高自賞。<br />\n9。唔識得去欣賞別人&lt;&lt;唔洗我講咁多啦<br />\n10。唔去打埋自己的外表同內在， 人靠衣裝佛靠金裝，修養同外表一樣咁重要。<br />\n<br />\n如果中哂十樣，你一定係垃圾中嘅垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1f73d6404b76545c00a81c4a3d7434951438001","tid":368051,"uid":27210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T09:51:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>八婆格 玩office politics 搵唔到錢 老婆奴 溝唔到女 見識少</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n啲臭雞格嘅女真係想大巴大巴煎死佢地<br />\n<br />\n搵唔到錢呢個有待商榷<br />\n<br />\n呀媽話怕老婆會發達<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  我想發達<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n溝唔到女，唉這些機會<br />\n<br />\n見識少呢樣真，明明世界咁大，都唔識去睇多啲唔同嘅野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n八婆格男人呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n做office大撚把<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4588c464839413444bde5bd7266eabf15d6e0c7","tid":368051,"uid":71181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T09:52:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"29ea18c287629aa11077ba85cc53bbaffcc58e7b","tid":368051,"uid":76098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T09:53:08.000Z","msg":"just like me"},{"pid":"f2eeab1cabeaab180adacbbbdc229adfca144696","tid":368051,"uid":68547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T09:55:05.000Z","msg":"唔上進 安穩現狀<br />\n人工停滯 職級停留<br />\n靠父母 唔打算有樓"},{"pid":"c9a92daf92c39ea08684615d69d02376065c9def","tid":368051,"uid":58841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T13:23:45.000Z","msg":"垃圾同廢柴係兩樣野黎架喎<br />\n垃圾無得救<br />\n廢柴起碼仲可以燒一陣"},{"pid":"222a3a2f40b45d4b3e6e78443e72079ae11cbdd9","tid":368051,"uid":72831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T13:47:02.000Z","msg":"三年前<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"></span>"},{"pid":"0b09937b765fadf5a0430c69828bd19024b8129c","tid":368051,"uid":27210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T13:48: